mindmap
  root((AI Maturity Models))
    Maturity Stages
      Ad Hoc
        Scattered pilots, no coordination
      Experimental
        Structured but fragmented
      Operational
        Standards exist, most plateau here
      Strategic
        AI aligned with business roadmap
      Transformational
        AI shapes the business model
    Assessment Dimensions
      Strategy and Leadership
        Defined AI strategy, executive understanding
      Data Infrastructure
        Quality, accessibility, compliance
      Talent and Structure
        Right people, embedded not siloed
      Technology and Toolchain
        MLOps maturity, monitoring at scale
      Risk and Ethics
        Bias management, red teaming, regulation
      Process Integration
        KPI linkage, feedback loops, trust
    Organizational Archetypes
      Tech-Forward
        Fast adoption, later standardization
      Compliance-Heavy
        Governance first, resilient foundations
      Federated
        Uneven evolution, orchestrated coordination
      Centralized
        Faster standards, bottleneck risk
    Strategic Application
      Prioritization
        Target highest-leverage gaps
      Realistic Timelines
        Phased advancement, not overreach
      Common Language
        Bridge technical and business teams
      Accountability
        Baselines, benchmarks, progress reporting